Usage: add_to_collection [-help] <base_collection> <second_collection_or_list>
                         [-unique]

-help                           # Prints out the command usage
<base_collection>               # Base collection of objects (string, required)
<second_collection_or_list>     # Second collection of objects, or an object
                                # list (string, required)
-unique                         # Retains any duplicate objects that already
                                # exist in the base collection (bool, optional)